div.h1: Redirect by file, user, page, revision, or log ID

div.p: This special page redirects to a file (given the filename), a page (given a revision ID or page ID), a user page (given a numeric user ID), or a log entry (given the log ID). Usage: Special:Redirect/file/Example.jpg, Special:Redirect/page/64308, Special:Redirect/revision/328429, Special:Redirect/user/101, or Special:Redirect/logid/186.
